2.3 DUIM-Geometry Module

region-set?

Generic function

Summary

Returns #t if its argument is a region set.

Signature

region-set? object => boolean

Arguments

object
An instance of type <object>.

Values

boolean
An instance of type <boolean>.

Library

duim-geometry

Module

duim-geometry

Description

Returns #t if object is a region set, otherwise returns #f.

See also

<region-set>, page 56
